        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 text-secondary">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="font-display text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-light leading-relaxed text-text">To create meaningful encounters between artworks, artists, and audiences—fostering conversations that transcend geographical and cultural boundaries while contributing to the global discourse on contemporary art.</p>
